abstract: Outside Camp Randall Stadium, Big Ten Commissioner Jim Delany seemed to relish the scene he had helped create.
snippet: Outside Camp Randall Stadium, Big Ten Commissioner Jim Delany seemed to relish the scene he had helped create.
lead_paragraph: MADISON, Wis. - Big Ten Commissioner Jim Delany spent about an hour before Nebraska's debut game in the Big Ten taking pictures with Cornhusker fans.

headline.main: Big Ten Chief Is Thanked In Wisconsin
